* 5K Awards List
*
* Purpose:          Generates the complete awards listing for the 5K race.
*                   Run after results are validated and before the awards ceremony.
*
* Flow:
*   1. OVERHDR.RSM        -- Prints the awards header and resets any prior excludes.
*   2. @OVERALL.RSM       -- Lists top N overall winners (male & female) and excludes them.
*   3. AGERES.RSM         -- Lists top N in each age group (overall winners already excluded).
*   4. FormFeedAtEnd.rsm  -- Optional "Form feed at end" when needed.
*
* To customize:
*   - Change the first number in each line to adjust how many winners per category.
*   - Add or remove AGERES.RSM lines to change age group brackets.
*
OVERHDR.RSM
* Overall male and female awards (top 3 each)
@OVERALL.RSM 3 FEMALE F
@OVERALL.RSM 3 MALE   M
* Age group awards (top 3 each, overall winners excluded)
AGERES.RSM 3 FEMALE F 1  19
AGERES.RSM 3 MALE   M 1  19
AGERES.RSM 3 FEMALE F 20 29
AGERES.RSM 3 MALE   M 20 29

AGERES.RSM 3 FEMALE F 30 39
AGERES.RSM 3 MALE   M 30 39

AGERES.RSM 3 FEMALE F 40 49
AGERES.RSM 3 MALE   M 40 49
AGERES.RSM 3 FEMALE F 50 59
AGERES.RSM 3 MALE   M 50 59
AGERES.RSM 3 FEMALE F 60 99
AGERES.RSM 3 MALE   M 60 99
FormFeedAtEnd.rsm
